author: The Babylon Bee
description:
These parents just want to let their little one learn basic shapes and colors, but he's about to get a lesson in standing up to patriarchal power structures through expressions of gender non-conformity. Not good.

Family entertainment should be entertainment! Meet @mechwestshow, the new all-ages action adventure series about kids and robots in the Old West. Watch it right on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/@mechwestshow 

#tvshow #comedy #babylonbee
title: Parents Struggle To Find Non-Woke Kid Shows
